Class Graph.Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • environment.GUI.views.Graph.Entry
  • Enclosing class:
    Graph

    private class Graph.Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores all the Statistics from the Station that is passed to the Graph each tick of the Simulator.

    09/04/17
    Author:
    Joshua_Eddy
